---
title: Beef Rump & Homestyle Gravy with Roasted Potatoes & Garlicky Veggies
description: This meal should be right at home at your place tonight. A nice piece of steak, smothered in a warm homestyle gravy and served with crispy roasted potatoes. Sometimes it’s hard to beat classic and simple.

*Unfortunately, this week's creamy peppercorn sauce was in short supply, so we've replaced it with homestyle gravy. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
